## Article Content

CLIENTS
CLIENT LIST
Exporting Your Client List

To export your client list, open the Clients app and select Options. Update the filters as needed and select Download to export the client list as a CSV file.

Note: 

The export option is only available in the desktop app and is not available in the mobile app.
